title: Adam Rippon
description: Samantha Bee sits down with Olympian Adam Rippon to discuss how to choose the music for your figure skating routine, begging people not to vote for Bob Dole, and the pivot from being an athlete to being an entertainer.
author: fullrelease@sambee.com (Samantha Bee)
